longBusinessSummary: SNP Schneider-Neureither & Partner SE provides software products and software-related consulting services worldwide. It operates through two segments, Services and Software. The Services segment offers consulting and training services, such as traditional SAP consulting and implementation, as well as hosting, cloud, and application management services. The Software segment provides CrystalBridge, a data transformation platform for the analysis, planning, and implementation of IT data transformations in an enterprise resource planning environment. This segment also licenses and sells software, as well as offers maintenance services, including software updates, upgrades and enhancements, and technical product support services. SNP Schneider-Neureither & Partner SE was founded in 1994 and is headquartered in Heidelberg, Germany.
